Package com.library.utils.tableviews

Class BookTreeTableViewBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.library.utils.tableviews.BookTreeTableViewBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeTableViewBuilder<Book>
public class BookTreeTableViewBuilder extends Object implements TreeTableViewBuilder<Book>
The BookTreeTableViewBuilder class implements the TreeTableViewBuilder interface to create and configure JavaFX TreeTableView columns for the Book entity. It defines columns for book properties such as title, author, genre, status, times used, and published year.
